    {
      "text": "UFO: A Day in the Life is an adventure puzzle game developed by Love-de-Lic and published by ASCII Entertainment for the PlayStation exclusively in Japan.\nHamster announced the game to be re-released under the Console Archives label for Nintendo Switch 2 and PlayStation 5 at an unspecified date.",
